v1.07 (2021-10-12)
- The regex searching for the path to Ghostscript has been fixed.
  See the issue #5 for details.

v1.06 (2020-05-04)
- Toolset.pm is now directly imported into the namespace.

v1.06 (2020-05-03)
- .svg conversion commands added.

v1.05 (2019-05-16)
- Whether or not to crop EPS files can be selected via the cmd-line opt.

v1.04 (2019-04-24)
- The version of converted PDF files can now be specified via the cmd-line opt.

v1.03 (2019-03-26)
- Routines of Toolset.pm have been embedded in the source code.

v1.02 (2019-03-23)
- Source code reorganized
- Fonts are now embedded in the pdfwrite device
